query:
SELECT r.id, r.title, r.flockId, r.status, r.dueDate 
FROM reminders r 
LEFT JOIN flocks f ON r.flockId = f.id 
WHERE r.flockId IS NOT NULL AND f.id IS NULL
LIMIT 20
